        "Confidential client data has been transmitted to a third-party service provider (Anthropic) without the client's knowledge or consent — this may violate the client's confidentiality agreement with the company, applicable data protection regulations, and professional standards. The company's acceptable use policy for AI tools should explicitly specify what categories of data may not be uploaded to external AI services.",
