        "Implement a semantic cache — embed incoming queries, compare to cached query embeddings, and return cached responses when similarity exceeds a threshold. For the 60% of calls with similar inputs, the cache eliminates the API call entirely, reducing monthly call volume toward 200,000 without changing the output quality for unique queries.",
